_sText:
jb_lost_planet_redux

A port of a wonderful CSGO jailbreak map made by Riczz.=D for the 2018 CSGO jailbreak mapping contest, which was later updated after winning 4th place in the contest.

 

List of games:

  • Dropdown
  • Tic-Tac-Toe
  • Long jump
  • Soccer
  • Two-Player Race
  • KZ with LJ room
  • Wipeout
  • Jumprope
  • Antigravity Chamber
  • Spleef
  • Classic Roulette
  • Melon Roulette
  • Bhop
  • Strafe Race
  • Deathcube
  • Glass Break Race
  • 4 Corners
  • Volleyball

Features:

  • 3 rebel paths & gun cells
  • Disco with 4 songs
  • Secret weapon pickups with various spawn options
  • Swimming pool
  • Beautiful scenery
  • Radar
  • Healer room
  • Boosters
